# Driver Qualification File Management

## Purpose

This document establishes the requirements for maintaining Driver Qualification Files (DQFs).

The objective is to ensure compliance with FMCSA regulations and Amazon Freight Partner requirements.

---

# DQ File Requirements

Each driver shall have a Driver Qualification File containing required documentation.

---

# Required Documents

## Employment Application

Maintain current copy.

---

## Motor Vehicle Record (MVR)

Initial review prior to hire.

Annual review thereafter.

---

## CDL Verification

Maintain current copy of CDL.

---

## Medical Examiner's Certificate

Maintain current medical card.

Track expiration dates.

---

## Road Test Certificate

Maintain if applicable.

---

## Employment Verification

Maintain prior employer verification records.

---

## Safety Performance History

Maintain required documentation.

---

# Annual Review

Complete annual review of:

- MVR
- Medical qualification
- Driver performance

---

# Record Retention

Maintain records according to applicable FMCSA requirements.

---

# Objective

Maintain complete and audit-ready Driver Qualification Files.
